articles.title: Is the AI bubble bursting?
articles.description: With a P/E ratio of 50 vs. the market's 30, AI companies are priced for exponential growth that rivals a risk-free bond yield. Investors face the same danger as the dot-com era: a transformative technology (AI) can exist alongside an unsustainable stock market bubble.

articles.description: Dr. Deepak Byotra deepak.byotra@smvdu.ac.in India is standing at a crucial turning point in its development journey.
